    </xsd:documentation>

    <xsd:documentation xml:lang="en-US">
Element types and definitions for an Assessment Item Usage Statistic XML document.  These types are for inclusion in other SAAIF XML schemata.  The schema is not namespaced and is unqualified.
    </xsd:documentation>

    <xsd:documentation xml:lang="en-US">
An Assessment Item Usage Statistic XML document captures data about the use of an assessment item.  The assessment item usage statistics are represented as a collection of subelements of the statistic element.  The statistic element is the root of the subtree of elements.  The statistic element is one of the subelements of an assessment item.
    </xsd:documentation>

